"region with reliable machinery for years. Our journey started in a small "
"workshop, with a simple idea: to give the farmer equipment they can trust "
"and support they can count on when it matters most."

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_story.html:18
msgid ""
"Vremenom smo izrasli u prepoznatljivog partnera za traktore, priključnu "
"opremu, radne mašine i polovnu mehanizaciju. Svaki proizvod biramo pažljivo, "
"a svakog kupca pratimo i posle prodaje — jer verujemo da se poverenje gradi "
"rezultatima na polju, a ne obećanjima."
msgstr ""
"Over time we have grown into a recognized partner for tractors, attachment "
"equipment, work machines and used machinery. We choose every product "
"carefully, and we follow up with every customer after the sale too — because "
"we believe trust is built on results in the field, not on promises."

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_story.html:21
msgid ""
"Danas, kao i prvog dana, vodi nas ista vrednost: prijatelj koji razume "
"zemlju. Tu smo da rastemo zajedno sa vama, sezonu za sezonom."
msgstr ""
"Today, as on the first day, the same value guides us: a friend who "
"understands the land. We are here to grow together with you, season after "
"season."

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:8
msgid "VREMENSKA LENTA"
msgstr "TIMELINE"

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:10
msgid "Naš put kroz godine"
msgstr "Our journey through the years"

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:17
msgid "Početak priče"
msgstr "The beginning of the story"

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:20
msgid ""
"Iz male porodične radionice krećemo sa prodajom i servisom poljoprivredne "
"mehanizacije, sa fokusom na domaćine kojima je pouzdanost važnija od svega."
msgstr ""
"From a small family workshop we start selling and servicing agricultural "
"machinery, focusing on farmers for whom reliability matters above all."

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:27
msgid "Širenje ponude"
msgstr "Expanding the offer"

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:30
msgid ""
"Proširujemo asortiman na priključnu opremu i radne mašine vodećih brendova i "
"otvaramo veći prodajno-servisni prostor za rastuću mrežu kupaca."
msgstr ""
"We expand our range with attachment equipment and work machines from leading "
"brands and open a larger sales-and-service space for our growing network of "
"customers."

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:37
msgid "Pouzdan partner regiona"
msgstr "A reliable partner for the region"

#: templates/pages/partials/_about_timeline.html:40
msgid ""
"Danas smo prepoznatljiv partner poljoprivrednika širom regiona — sa "
"kompletnom ponudom mehanizacije, polovne opreme i podrškom koja traje i "
"posle prodaje."
msgstr ""
"Today we are a recognized partner of farmers across the region — with a "
"complete offer of machinery, used equipment and support that lasts beyond "
"the sale."

